Package: memgraph-mage
Architecture: @ARCH@
Replaces: memgraph
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, memgraph, libcurl4, libpython3.12, openssl, python3, python3-pip, python3-setuptools, adduser, libgomp1, libaio1t64, libatomic1, libdw1t64 | libdw1
Description: Extra query modules for Memgraph
 Additional query modules for Memgraph, installed under
 /usr/lib/memgraph/query_modules/.

Package: memgraph-mage-debuginfo
Architecture: @ARCH@
Section: debug
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, memgraph-mage (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for memgraph-mage
 Sidecar .debug files for the MAGE query modules, produced by
 objcopy --only-keep-debug at build time. Install alongside
 memgraph-mage for symbolicated stack traces; gdb auto-locates
 each .debug file via .gnu_debuglink next to the corresponding
 .so.
